bsu.famcs.airline.airplanes

Class CargoAirplane

  • java.lang.Object
    • bsu.famcs.airline.airplanes.Airplane
      • bsu.famcs.airline.airplanes.CargoAirplane

  • public class CargoAirplane
extends Airplane
    This class is created for work with cargo airplanes. It extends class Airplane and have only one unique field for volume of cargo. This class implemets getters and setters for fields and method toString().
